{"tid":306851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【贏在起跑線】點解好少見愛因斯坦病？ 牛津新研究：IQ高都無咁易病","createTime":"2017-07-03T01:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T03:48:48.000Z","uid":13468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b14fac6e977573c2a0577a81993e9fa09a259150","tid":306851,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:02:35.000Z","msg":"【贏在起跑線】點解好少見愛因斯坦病？ 牛津新研究：IQ高都無咁易病<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56897591&amp;category_guid=10829392&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56897591%26category_guid%3D10829392%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170703&d=zvgcQPVlc%2F91PamQ6ZY%2FGP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=a77a136c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56897591%26category_guid%3D10829392%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170703&h=4a346e97\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56897591&amp;category_guid=10829392&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170703</a><br />\n<br />\n在歷史上的確甚少提到愛因斯坦生病，到底是智商作怪，還是「得閒死唔得閒病」呢？<br />\n<br />\n要贏在起跑線，其實不單要贏在射精前，根本就要「贏在智商前」，但難道給小朋友吃「聰明藥」就會變聰明？智商是天生的，愛因斯坦的智商（IQ）估計就有160至190左右，雖然愛因斯坦在76歲因腹主動脈瘤破裂而內出血死亡，但智商的確有為他的前半生帶來健康。據最新一期《英國醫學期刊》（British Medical Journal）內一份有關智商、患病和壽命的研究指，原來智商高生病機會較低，壽命亦因而比較長。<br />\n<br />\n英國牛津大學和蘇格蘭愛丁堡大學 （University of Edinburgh）的學者追蹤了65,765個在1936年蘇格蘭出生的男女，根據他們在11歲的智商測試成績，並了解他們的身體狀況至2015年底，結果發現，智商高的男女在79歲前有較低的死亡風險，患上呼吸系统疾病的機會減少28%；患上呼冠心病的機會減少25%；患上因吸煙而引發的疾病減少24%，其餘還有消化系統疾病和老人癡呆的患病機會亦有所降低。在今期《英》評論該研究的瑞典學者指，由於研究未有深入調查受訪者的智商，故未能肯定成因，但相信可能與基因有關。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<br />\n<br />\nDaniel Falkstedt, Anton C J Lager. Higher IQ in childhood is linked to a longer life. BMJ, 2017; j2932 DOI: 10.1136/bmj.j2932<br />\n<br />\nCatherine M Calvin, G David Batty, Geoff Der, Caroline E Brett, Adele Taylor, Alison Pattie, Iva Čukić, Ian J Deary. Childhood intelligence in relation to major causes of death in 68 year follow-up: prospective population study. BMJ, 2017; j2708 DOI: 10.1136/bmj.j2708"},{"pid":"d6ef3c4b357aab51408a220be9f8dcaa5d6bba3e","tid":306851,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:03:24.000Z","msg":"霍金IQ低?"},{"pid":"e1abadd5e816126e59cf43875e4b244445a03d4d","tid":306851,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:14:34.000Z","msg":"東亞病夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba20d11d38259ae0e442e8f3d85054fe1bdfcf35","tid":306851,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:19:20.000Z","msg":"其實想知好耐，會員血緣詛咒到底係點樣做到如此置身事外既呢，佢唔係華人?"},{"pid":"4bee99d67d0a0d121d8ef5300c5d73fd9943fa02","tid":306851,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:20:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>霍金IQ低?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/